ext\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"code\"}],\"text\":\"git show @~3\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" 等价于 \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"code\"}],\"text\":\"git show HEAD~3\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"。\"}]},{\"type\":\"heading\",\"attrs\":{\"level\":3,\"id\":\"查看命令帮助\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"查看命令帮助\"}]},{\"type\":\"bulletList\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"listItem\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"任何命令加 \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"code\"}],\"text\":\"--help\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" 可查看详细文档，如 \"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"code\"}],\"text\":\"git add --help\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"。\"}]}]}]}]}","title":"Git 常用指令","tags":["Tools","github"],"updateTime":1773817712447,"createTime":1773817710426,"draft":false,"intro":"然后在 ~/.gitignore_global 中写入忽略规则。","html":"<h1 level=\"1\" id=\"Git-常用指令\">Git 常用指令</h1><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"-基础配置与初始化\"> 基础配置与初始化</h2><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"用户信息\">用户信息</h3><ul><li><p><strong>设置</strong>（全局）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">arduino</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-arduino\">git config --global user.name <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;你的名字&quot;</span>\ngit config --global user.email <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>查看</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">arduino</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-arduino\">git config user.name\ngit config user.email\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"别名配置\">别名配置</h3><ul><li><p><strong>设置别名</strong>（以 <code>st</code> 代替 <code>status</code> 为例）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">csharp</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">git config --<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">global</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">alias</span>.st status\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>常用别名示例</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">perl</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-perl\">git config --global alias.co checkout\ngit config --global alias.br branch\ngit config --global alias.ci commit\ngit config --global alias.lg <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;log --color --graph --pretty=format:&apos;%Cred%h<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%Creset</span> -<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%C</span>(yellow)%d<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%Creset</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%s</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%Cgreen</span>(<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%cr</span>) <span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%C</span>(bold blue)&lt;<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%an</span>&gt;<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">%Creset</span>&apos; --abbrev-commit&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"其他全局配置\">其他全局配置</h3><ul><li><p><strong>启用颜色输出</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">arduino</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-arduino\">git config --global color.ui <span class=\"hljs-literal\" class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>全局忽略文件配置</strong></p><p>可以创建一个全局的 <code>.gitignore_global</code> 文件，忽略所有仓库都通用的文件（如编辑器临时文件、操作系统生成的文件等）。</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">lua</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-lua\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">config</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\">--global core.excludesfile ~/.gitignore_global</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><p>然后在 <code>~/.gitignore_global</code> 中写入忽略规则。</p><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"初始化仓库\">初始化仓库</h3><ul><li><p><strong>将当前目录变为 Git 仓库</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">csharp</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">init</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>查看当前目录</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">pwd</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"生成-SSH-Key用于远程连接\">生成 SSH Key（用于远程连接）</h3><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">perl</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-perl\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;your_email<span class=\"hljs-variable\" class=\"hljs-variable\">@example</span>.com&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"文件操作添加删除移动\">文件操作：添加、删除、移动</h2><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"添加文件到暂存区git-add\">添加文件到暂存区（<code>git add</code>）</h3><p>命令说明<code>git add &lt;file&gt;</code>添加指定文件<code>git add .</code>添加当前目录所有变更（包括新增、修改、删除）<code>git add -A</code>等同于 <code>git add --all</code>，添加所有变更（工作区根目录下所有变更） <strong>注</strong>：在 Git 2.x 中无论当前目录位置都会添加全部变更，旧版行为略有不同，推荐直接使用 <code>--all</code> 避免歧义。<code>git add -u</code>只添加已跟踪文件的修改（不处理未跟踪文件）<code>git add -p</code>交互式选择部分修改添加<code>git add -i</code>进入交互式添加模式<code>git add -f</code>强制添加被 <code>.gitignore</code> 忽略的文件</p><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"删除文件git-rm\">删除文件（<code>git rm</code>）</h3><ul><li><p><strong>删除工作区文件并暂存删除操作</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">rm</span> &lt;file&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>仅从 Git 中删除（保留本地文件）</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">rm</span> --cached &lt;file&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>递归删除目录</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">rm</span> -r &lt;<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">dir</span>&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>强制删除</strong>（文件有未提交修改时）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">rm</span> -f &lt;file&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"移动或重命名文件git-mv\">移动或重命名文件（<code>git mv</code>）</h3><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">mv</span> &lt;old-name&gt; &lt;new-name&gt; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 重命名文件并自动暂存</span>\ngit <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">mv</span> &lt;file&gt; &lt;destination&gt;/ &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 移动文件到其他目录</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><p>该命令相当于运行了 <code>mv</code> 命令后执行了 <code>git add</code> 和 <code>git rm</code>，简化了操作。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"提交与查看历史\">提交与查看历史</h2><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"提交暂存区内容git-commit\">提交暂存区内容（<code>git commit</code>）</h3><ul><li><p><strong>标准提交</strong>（打开编辑器输入信息）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">sql</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-sql\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>直接提交带消息</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">sql</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-sql\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span>m &quot;提交说明&quot;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>跳过暂存区，直接提交已跟踪文件的修改</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">sql</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-sql\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span>a <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span>m &quot;提交说明&quot;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>修改最近一次提交</strong>（可修改信息或补充文件）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">sql</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-sql\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\">--amend</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>指定作者/日期</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">ini</div><div class=\"wrapper\">