adonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">log</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>单行简洁显示</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">lua</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-lua\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">log</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\">--oneline</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>图形化显示分支合并图</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">css</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-css\">git log <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">--graph</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">--pretty</span>=oneline <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">--abbrev-commit</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>显示最近 N 条</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">log</span> -n 5\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>显示每次提交的差异</strong>：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">log</span> -p\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>显示统计信息</strong>：</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">log</span> --<span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">stat</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>高级筛选</strong></p><ul><li><p>按提交信息关键词过滤</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">ini</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-ini\">git log <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">--grep</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;关键词&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p>按代码变更内容搜索（pickaxe）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\" class=\"hljs-built_in\">log</span> -S<span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;要搜索的代码片段&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"其他查看命令\">其他查看命令</h3><ul><li><p><strong>逐行追溯文件</strong>（谁在什么时候修改了哪一行）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">xml</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-xml\">git blame <span class=\"hljs-tag\" class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\" class=\"hljs-name\">file</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>生成简短的提交统计</strong>（用于快速发布日志）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">bash</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">git shortlog\ngit shortlog -sn &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 按提交数量排序显示贡献者</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>在版本库中搜索文本</strong>（比系统 <code>grep</code> 更快，且只搜索 tracked 文件）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">perl</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-perl\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">grep</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;要搜索的文字&quot;</span>\ngit <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">grep</span> -n <span class=\"hljs-string\" class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;文字&quot;</span> &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 显示行号</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"查看操作历史git-reflog\">查看操作历史（<code>git reflog</code>）</h3><ul><li><p><strong>记录所有 HEAD 移动历史，可用于找回丢失的提交</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div><p><strong>提示</strong>：<code>@</code> 是 HEAD 的简写，例如 <code>git show @{yesterday}</code> 可查看昨天 HEAD 指向的提交。</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"比较差异git-diff\">比较差异（<code>git diff</code>）</h2><p>命令作用<code>git diff</code>工作区 vs 暂存区<code>git diff --staged</code> 或 <code>--cached</code>暂存区 vs 最新提交（HEAD）<code>git diff HEAD</code>工作区 vs 最新提交（所有未提交修改）<code>git diff &lt;commit1&gt; &lt;commit2&gt;</code>两个提交之间的差异<code>git diff &lt;branch1&gt; &lt;branch2&gt;</code>两个分支之间的差异<code>git diff -- &lt;file&gt;</code>查看某个文件的修改<code>git diff --stat</code>仅显示统计信息<code>git diff --name-only</code>仅显示文件名<code>git diff --word-diff</code>按单词显示差异<code>git diff -w</code>忽略空格差异</p><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"撤销与恢复\">撤销与恢复</h2><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"工作区修改的撤销\">工作区修改的撤销</h3><ul><li><p><strong>丢弃单个文件的修改</strong>（不可恢复）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">lua</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-lua\">git checkout <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\">-- &lt;file&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>丢弃所有工作区修改</strong>（慎用）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">text</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-erlang\">git checkout .\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>新版推荐</strong>（<code>git restore</code>）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">xml</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-xml\">git restore <span class=\"hljs-tag\" class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\" class=\"hljs-name\">file</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"暂存区修改的撤销\">暂存区修改的撤销</h3><ul><li><p><strong>将文件从暂存区移回工作区</strong>（取消 <code>git add</code>）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">perl</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-perl\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">reset</span> HEAD &lt;file&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>取消所有暂存</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">perl</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-perl\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">reset</span> HEAD .\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>新版推荐</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">css</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-css\">git restore <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">--staged</span> &lt;file&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"版本回退git-reset\">版本回退（<code>git reset</code>）</h3><p><code>git reset</code> 有三种主要模式：</p><ul><li><p><code>--soft</code>：仅移动 HEAD 指针，<strong>保留暂存区和工作区</strong>（即撤销提交，但修改仍暂存）</p></li><li><p><code>--mixed</code>（默认）：移动 HEAD，<strong>清空暂存区但保留工作区</strong>（撤销提交和暂存，修改仍在工作区）</p></li><li><p><code>--hard</code>：移动 HEAD，<strong>清空暂存区并丢弃工作区修改</strong>（彻底回到指定提交的状态，慎用）</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>回退到上一个版本</strong>（保留工作区修改）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">perl</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-perl\">git <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">reset</span> --soft HEAD^ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 保留暂存区</span>\ngit <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">reset</span> --mixed HEAD^ &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\"># 保留工作区，清空暂存区（默认）</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>彻底回退到指定提交</strong>（丢弃之后的所有修改）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">css</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-css\">git reset <span class=\"hljs-attr\" class=\"hljs-attr\">--hard</span> &lt;commit-id&gt;\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>回退部分文件到指定版本</strong>（不影响其他文件）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">sql</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-sql\">git checkout <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span><span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span>id<span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\">-- &lt;file&gt;</span>\ngit <span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span>m &quot;回退文件&quot;\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"恢复误删的文件\">恢复误删的文件</h3><ul><li><p><strong>从版本库恢复</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">lua</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-lua\">git checkout <span class=\"hljs-comment\" class=\"hljs-comment\">-- &lt;file&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"使用-git-revert-安全撤销合并提交\">使用 <code>git revert</code> 安全撤销合并提交</h3><ul><li><p><strong>创建一个反向提交</strong>（推荐用于已推送的合并）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">sql</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-sql\">git revert <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span>m <span class=\"hljs-number\" class=\"hljs-number\">1</span> <span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">merge</span><span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">-</span><span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">commit</span><span class=\"hljs-operator\" class=\"hljs-operator\">&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><h2 level=\"2\" id=\"分支管理\">分支管理</h2><h3 level=\"3\" id=\"创建与切换分支\">创建与切换分支</h3><ul><li><p><strong>传统方式</strong></p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p></p></li></ul><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">csharp</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code class=\"language-csharp\">git branch &lt;branch-name&gt; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span class=\"hljs-meta\" class=\"hljs-meta\"># 创建分支</span>\ngit checkout &lt;branch-name&gt; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-meta\" class=\"hljs-meta\"># 切换分支</span>\ngit checkout -b &lt;<span class=\"hljs-keyword\" class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span>-branch&gt; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span class=\"hljs-meta\" class=\"hljs-meta\"># 创建并切换</span>\n</code></pre></div></div><ul><li><p><strong>新版方式</strong>（<code>git switch</code>）</p><div class=\"llt-code readonly\"><div class=\"language\">auto</div><div class=\"wrapper\"><pre><code></code></pre></div></div></li></ul><ul><li><p